  "title": "Chef",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p><ul><li><p>Prepare and cook authentic Korean dishes.</p></li><li><p>Ensure all dishes are prepared to the highest quality standards and within the recipes.</p></li><li><p>Manage kitchen operations, including inventory and staff supervision.</p></li><li><p>Adhere to hygiene and food safety regulations, ensuring a clean and safe kitchen environment.</p></li><li><p>Assist in menu development and cost control.</p></li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li><p>Proven experience as a Chef.</p></li><li><p>Culinary diploma or equivalent certification.</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of cooking techniques and ingredients.</p></li><li><p>Strong organizational and leadership skills.</p></li><li><p>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment, including evenings, weekends and holidays.</p></li></ul><p>Aurora Asia Pacific (21C0671)|Stephanie (R21100585)</p>",
